extends ../layout

block content
    h1 Lottery Tool
    p
        | This is our own provably fair lottery tool. You can use this tool to create your own lotteries and show they're provably fair by linking to our&nbsp;
        a(href="https://github.com/StefanDorresteijn/provably") source code
    .row
        .col-md-9
            h3 Our lottery system
            p To create a lottery on our site, simply fill in a name, the maximum entries, the amount of winners your lottery will have and when your lottery will end. You'll also need to fill in a secret email address and secret key which you'll use to add entries to your lottery.
            form(action="/api/v1/lottery_tool/" method="post" id="lottery_form")
                .form-group
                        label(for="lottery_tool_name") Lottery Name
                        input.form-control(type="text" id="lottery_tool_name" name="name")
                .form-group
                    label(for="lottery_tool_email") Email
                    input.form-control(type="email" id="lottery_tool_email" name="email")
                .form-group
                    label(for="lottery_tool_secret_key") Secret Key
                    input.form-control(type="text" id="lottery_tool_secret_key" name="secret_key")
                .form-group
                    label(for="lottery_tool_max_entries") Maxmimum entries
                    input.form-control(type="number" id="lottery_tool_max_entries" name="max_entries")
                .form-group
                    label(for="lottery_tool_amount_of_winners") Amount of Winners
                    input.form-control(type="number" id="lottery_tool_amount_of_winners" name="amount_of_winners")
                .form-group
                    label(for="lottery_tool_end_date") End Date
                    input.form-control.datetimepicker(type="text" id="lottery_tool_end_date" name="end_time")
                button.btn.btn-default(type="submit") Save Lottery
        .col-md-3
            h3 Latest draws
            #app